<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē nāgavahnitriśaśiparimitē jyēṣṭhamāsē budāhē
<lb n="2"/>rākāyāṁ puppamālāmanudinamapi cākhaṁḍamēkaṁ pradīpaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="3"/>prādādiṣṭa<unclear>r</unclear>ttasi<unclear>ddhyai</unclear> harigiripatayē śrīnṛsiṁhāya cētyā śrīmā<supplied reason="omitted">N</supplied> saṁtēśvarā
<lb n="4"/>ryō gaṇakakulavarō bhānudēvasya rājñaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbu 1338 gu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nēṁṭi jyēṣṭha śuddha vunnema bu<supplied reason="omitted">dha</supplied>varanāḍu siṁhādrināthanikini kaliṁgapa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rīkṣa śrīkaraṇapaṭṭānayeṁḍu śrīsaṁtēśvaramahāsēnāpati tanakunu
<lb n="7"/>Iṣṭharttasiddhigānu nityamunnu tri<unclear>ru</unclear>vajjā<unclear>ma</unclear>vasaramaṁdu lāgi
<lb n="8"/>gānu doṁḍavanamāla 1 Okaṭi sanni<unclear>dhi</unclear>yaṁdu veluṁguṭakunu
<lb n="9"/>Akhaṁḍadīpamu 1 samarppiṁcenu Ī doṁḍapeṭṭanu bisāḷigaṁguku
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nu gaṭṭusahitamugānu <unclear>ga</unclear>ṁḍamāḍalu 10 peṭenu I Akhaṁḍadīpāna
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kai Annikhillārivaśānanu neI nela 1 kuṁcālu 7 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> peṭanu mōdālu
<lb n="12"/>50 vīri jītānaku puṭṭaṁḍu kṣētrānakai gaṁḍamāḍalu 25 peṭṭenu Ī jī
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ta manubhaviṁci Ācaṁdrārkkamugānu peṭṭuvaru; Ī dharmmamu śrīvai
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṣṇapa rakṣa śrīśrīśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
